{"tid":82540,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"一齊住得耐會淡？","createTime":"2017-01-16T04:40:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-16T17:04:51.000Z","uid":31940,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4f19adb43b25ed546ade98880a9daa6862135446","tid":82540,"uid":31940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T04:40:10.000Z","msg":"是咁的，女友係我屋企住左都成兩年，近年發展到連節日都冇一齊慶祝，各自各玩，係屋企亦唔會有咩戀愛既感覺。一齊出街都好似冇野做咁。<br />\n雙方都仲愛對方，但就真係好似冇女朋友咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就算去旅行或一段時間冇見，都可以冇聯繫，到底係咩玩法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?<br />\n<br />\n其實咁既情況，分開係咪對大家都好？<br />\n我feel到係其實雙方雖然有愛，但好似未到一個要過人世既點，而又唔捨得放棄。"},{"pid":"7f07c62d08de3b350c2fcb3d99c3a4f19ff63c51","tid":82540,"uid":27793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T04:51:53.000Z","msg":"分左會後悔"},{"pid":"dc00feb1cb1b1345629056098209a1378fdadb47","tid":82540,"uid":42009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T04:57:42.000Z","msg":"乜節日都唔一齊你確定你地係拍拖？"},{"pid":"cbeef72137bd9c69d7d1f3e90b9b02b315c9f33d","tid":82540,"uid":76105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T05:32:06.000Z","msg":"仲會唔會搞野？ <br />\n可能已經唔係愛, 只係想有個人陪自己"},{"pid":"177733e7caa591ec6414ebb9201a05e3b282b47e","tid":82540,"uid":54092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T05:37:06.000Z","msg":"其實結咗婚就會咁， 見得多就變親人，你仲想好似拍拖咁掛住對方？ 個環境都唔同咗啦！"},{"pid":"e543d4703063b1f3bb9d62edd85a99cde7a74486","tid":82540,"uid":31940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T06:28:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>分左會後悔</blockquote><br />\n或者大家會更好？<br />\n雖然係會後悔，但都係一段時間姐"},{"pid":"453bfe5a8e961a4bad765ed2f617bca95df39c81","tid":82540,"uid":31940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T06:29:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>乜節日都唔一齊你確定你地係拍拖？</blockquote><br />\nat least 名義上  係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a188f6660a3ef8c6a88cc009cf1f98dd61712388","tid":82540,"uid":31940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T06:30:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仲會唔會搞野？ <br />\n可能已經唔係愛, 只係想有個人陪自己</blockquote><br />\n少搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 成兩個月冇搞過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我都覺得係習慣左有個人陪下自己多過愛咁"},{"pid":"09cb51684681ec2e58cd3b839e76f85ed52d23bc","tid":82540,"uid":56329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T06:31:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>分左會後悔</blockquote><br />\n或者大家會更好？<br />\n雖然係會後悔，但都係一段時間姐</blockquote><br />\n我都分左手成過月都係咁&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申：一齊左三年幾"},{"pid":"e61480571948833d18e8868671c8a804a711908a","tid":82540,"uid":2832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T06:31:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>分左會後悔</blockquote><br />\n或者大家會更好？<br />\n雖然係會後悔，但都係一段時間姐</blockquote><br />\n咁你都決定咗啦，重問咩呀<br />\n分啦唔好累個女仔"},{"pid":"d19c6d1bba5488cd3a8fd21fa482a5aa2df5533c","tid":82540,"uid":31940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T06:32:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實結咗婚就會咁， 見得多就變親人，你仲想好似拍拖咁掛住對方？ 個環境都唔同咗啦！</blockquote><br />\n問題就係又未去到一齊面對生活咁，但已經變成親人咁，<br />\n有時我覺得佢係妹多過女朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d812829e702d67d194ae0d8569eb1f311f498c4c","tid":82540,"uid":31940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T06:34:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>分左會後悔</blockquote><br />\n或者大家會更好？<br />\n雖然係會後悔，但都係一段時間姐</blockquote><br />\n我都分左手成過月都係咁&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申：一齊左三年幾</blockquote><br />\n加油，始終習慣左係好難再適應一個人"},{"pid":"a012d9ead759185e2b273f8c088ad68ceeb73496","tid":82540,"uid":31940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T06:36:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>分左會後悔</blockquote><br />\n或者大家會更好？<br />\n雖然係會後悔，但都係一段時間姐</blockquote><br />\n咁你都決定咗啦，重問咩呀<br />\n分啦唔好累個女仔</blockquote><br />\n又冇話累唔累既，大家都係咁既feel<br />\n可能睇邊個開口先"},{"pid":"8753aee120770ad20a279c37b4d04ca583c5a04e","tid":82540,"uid":76105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T08:21:04.000Z","msg":"2個月無搞過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你有無試過對其他女仔有feel?<br />\n或者想意圖出軌 ？？"},{"pid":"b1a51fad2fda3e795a12ba7f2c96da74cb429bfa","tid":82540,"uid":30202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T08:36:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 住埋一齊有一年<br />\n<br />\n依然好享受兩個人一齊既時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a70be047ad39cbfe63cfa503d8647cb771bda23","tid":82540,"uid":31940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T08:45:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>2個月無搞過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你有無試過對其他女仔有feel?<br />\n或者想意圖出軌 ？？</blockquote><br />\n又唔會對其他有feel既<br />\n我唔知意圖出軌係點定義，<br />\n但我有諗過如果我同第二個一齊會點，而呢個只係幻想，冇實質一個女人"},{"pid":"c9631ece9ebbebd13cbdc7c446cb03b67994bcc2","tid":82540,"uid":16357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T15:31:44.000Z","msg":"情況差不多揮手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一齊左3年，而家先覺得大家發展得太快好似太遲..<br />\n到底係唔夾定淡左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而家都好煩惱分唔分...初戀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14b2f01966ab6aa87be4ef6bee6c8cc3a5815b12","tid":82540,"uid":6031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T16:12:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbce59e35474175855339095108f2f9bf954b938","tid":82540,"uid":19278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T17:01:36.000Z","msg":"一齊左幾多年？"},{"pid":"b019ec5e8d84ab91f69bf5e8b90d6eddc3f39292","tid":82540,"uid":20492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T17:04:51.000Z","msg":"一樣 岩岩一齊已經一齊住，已經唔會行街睇戲 最多有時出去樓下食飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}